"Groove Board" is a music rhythm game demo in SDL Perl, similar to
Dance Dance Revolution and StepMania.

Created by garu for the SDL Game Contest.


Music:
======

music.ogg is a poor-quality reencoding of the awesome
"Opening Day" song by ATOMSPLIT, released under a
Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 Unported
Licence (CC BY-SA 3.0).
You can support the band and download their full album
at http://www.jamendo.com/br/album/79105

Art:
====

I made the arrows myself using Gimp, and release them
under a Creative Commons Attribution 3.0 Unported
License (CC BY 3.0).

The background image is a 800x600 png reencoding of
"star in my bedroom" by Jennifer Boyer (Anosmia),
released under a Creative Commons Attribution 2.0
Generic License (CC BY 2.0).
http://www.flickr.com/photos/jenniferboyer/2110095567/


